query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sb_campaign_settings (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  campaign_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  account_id VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
  campaign_type ENUM('video', 'store_spotlight', 'product_collection') DEFAULT 'product_collection',
  landing_page_type ENUM('store', 'product_list', 'custom_url') DEFAULT 'store',
  brand_entity_id VARCHAR(50),
  auto_optimize_keywords TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0,
  auto_optimize_bids TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0,
  target_acos DECIMAL(10, 4),
  min_bid DECIMAL(10, 2),
  max_bid DECIMAL(10, 2),
  creative_optimization_enabled TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
